<h3 id="generalbass">Generalbass</h3>

<p class="figure"><img src="/assets/img/blog/dorico/Haendel_Sonate_D-Maj_HWV_271.png" alt="Original einer H√§ndel-Sonate D-Dur HWV 271" width="1167" height="432" loading="lazy" />
